    <introduction>
      <Value><![CDATA[<p>The <a rel="noopener" href="https://researcherdevelopmentconcordat.ac.uk/" target="_blank" title="Concordat to Support the Career Development of Researchers">Concordat to Support the Career Development of Researchers</a> sets out the expectations and responsibilities of researchers, their managers, employers and funders. By setting out clear expectations for researchers, research managers, research institutions, and funders of research, the Concordat aims to enhance the research workforce and thereby sustain research excellence in the UK, bringing benefits to the health, economy and wellbeing of our nation.</p>]]></Value>
